  "texts": [
    "We posit that this reverse engineering exercise might help improve the quality of original requirements; however, an in-depth investigation is required to establish this.",
    "Incorporating Broader System Information.",
    "The potential for LLMs to enhance TS generation through access to system architecture was discussed.",
    "Rory suggested, \"Based on my observations, it [the approach] can perform better in creation of TS if it would have access to the architecture schema of the used systems/applications,\" advocating for a more integrated approach to scenario generation.",
    "Experience and Human Oversight Matters."
